Monday, May 8, 1995

MOTION DOCKET

94-372. State v. Joseph. Allen County, No. 1-91-11.

This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Allen County. Upon consideration of appellant’s motion to strike merit brief of appellee,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion to strike merit brief of appellee be, and hereby is, denied, effective May 5, 1995.
